data.description: Enjoy "lake living" without the high taxes living just down the street from Jackson Lake and Reasor's Marina. Come see this spacious 5 Bedroom 4 bath home on an almost 2-acre lot on a cul-de-sac.  You will love this open floor plan with soaring ceilings and a separate dining room and office/Kids playroom right off the foyer.  The master suite has trey ceilings with a huge master bath with double vanities, a separate shower and a jetted tub.  Don't miss the incredibly large walk-in closet.  Downstairs you will find another bedroom and full bath.  Upstairs there are 3 more bedrooms with walk in closets and 2 bathrooms.  Not only is the house large and spacious, but so is the lot.  You have a porch on the front, a deck with a new hot tub on the back, a large concrete patio that has so many uses, and a fenced in back yard.  Bring the boat and the RV because there is plenty of room for it.  Must see to appreciate.
